// Holy Mark — Paladin marker applied by Smite / Spinning Hammer.
//
// Neutral: no DoT, no stat change, no element cancels it. It only marks a target so Paladin
// abilities can react to its presence (Spinning Hammer double damage, Hammer-of-Justice
// shockwave). Those consumers arrive with the Paladin (Phase 9); the marker itself is Phase-3
// data so the infrastructure is exercised.
(
    id: "holy_mark",
    display_name: "Holy Mark",
    stacking: RefreshOnReapply,
    base_duration_secs: 6.0,
)
